n        <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"img/h3_home_02.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <img src=\"img/h3_home_02.jpg\" width=\"670\" height=\"419\" alt=\"ケア用品・通販\" class=\"home-Service_Menu_Title_Image\"> </picture>\n      </h3>\n      <p class=\"home-Service_Menu_Text\">ケア用品のご案内と、手軽に購入できる販売サイトはこちら</p>\n      </a></li>\n    <li class=\"home-Service_Menu_Item\"><a href=\"https://www.sun-con.com/medical-comfirm/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"home-Service_Menu_Link\">\n      <h3 class=\"home-Service_Menu_Title\">\n        <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"img/h3_home_03.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <img src=\"img/h3_home_03.jpg\" width=\"670\" height=\"419\" alt=\"眼科医療機器\" class=\"home-Service_Menu_Title_Image\"> </picture>\n      </h3>\n      <p class=\"home-Service_Menu_Text\">医療関係者向けの製品案内です</p>\n      <ul class=\"home-Service_Menu_List\">\n        <li class=\"home-Service_Menu_List_Item\">オートレフトポグラファー</li>\n        <li class=\"home-Service_Menu_List_Item\">輪部支持型角膜形状異常眼用コンタクトレンズ</li>\n      </ul>\n      </a></li>\n    <li class=\"home-Service_Menu_Item\"><a href=\"partner/\" class=\"home-Service_Menu_Link\">\n      <h3 class=\"home-Service_Menu_Title\">\n        <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"img/h3_home_08.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <img src=\"img/h3_home_08.jpg\" width=\"670\" height=\"419\" alt=\"取扱施設検索\" class=\"home-Service_Menu_Title_Image\"> </picture>\n      </h3>\n      <p class=\"home-Service_Menu_Text\">弊社のコンタクトレンズの取扱施設を検索できます</p>\n      </a></li>\n    <li class=\"home-Service_Menu_Item\"><a href=\"howtouse/\" class=\"home-Service_Menu_Link\">\n      <h3 class=\"home-Service_Menu_Title\">\n        <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"img/h3_home_05.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <img src=\"img/h3_home_05.jpg\" width=\"670\" height=\"419\" alt=\"レンズの取扱い方法\" class=\"home-Service_Menu_Title_Image\"> </picture>\n      </h3>\n      <p class=\"home-Service_Menu_Text\">おすすめしているレンズの洗浄・保存方法をご案内しています</p>\n      <